## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1. Navigate to the new Alert Rules page.
2. Create a rule: *"Alert when mileage since brake check > 50"*.
3. Verify the alert appears in the Dashboard alerts and the Header notification bell.
4. Toggle the rule off and verify the alert disappears.
5. Delete the rule and confirm cleanup.
